name: Origins of Wilson (Prototype)
description:
This work is not final

In this demo, get to the green flag at the end of the game while avoiding and shooting enemies such as the Boarbots. Gates divide the level into various sublevels known as Areas which keep the enemies contained inside. 

Collect red Health crates to restore HP.
